## Limitations
The findings are based on interpretations of the Christian worldview and may not encompass all denominational perspectives within Christianity. Additionally, the sources used are limited to those available online and may not reflect the full spectrum of theological scholarship on the topic. Further research involving theological texts and expert interviews could provide a more comprehensive understanding.